      <description>&lt;p&gt;纯粹是闲出屁来了，最开始是因为在b站上看到有推销服务器的，恰巧我当时对这个比较感兴趣。&lt;strong&gt;于是我就在想我是不是也可以整一台云服务器&lt;/strong&gt;，当机立断就找妈妈要了100块钱，然后就在网上选到了阿里云的&lt;strong&gt;2h2g加峰值200m宽带&lt;/strong&gt;，&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-640.avif 640w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-640.webp 640w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-placeholder-320.jpg&#34;&#xA;    width=&#34;640&#34;&#xA;    height=&#34;1418&#34;&#xA;    data-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg 640w&#34;&#xA;    data-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-src=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg&#34;&#xA;    data-native-srcset=&#34;https://whyhzlab.github.io/2162063617.github.io/generated/image-variants/582aace8f948/3da8446b2836/responsive_content-fallback-640.jpg 640w&#34;&#xA;    sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    fetchpriority=&#34;low&#34;&#xA;    